pageContext.description: The edge of the butt has been broken, but a small section remains complete. There is an oval depression on each face just below the stop-ridge, one being more pronounced than the other.
pageContext.patina: Dark green on on the small areas of original surface which survive.,Brown/bright green, poor
pageContext.surface: Very rough because the original surface has largely been destroyed by corrosion.
pageContext.other: Length: 5 5/8" = 142.875 mm,Width: 2 1/8" at splay of blade = 53.975mm,Thickness: 1" = 25.4mm
